window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Lose yourself to the dark and glamorous underbelly of the Upper East Side in the final book in <i>USA Today</i> best-selling author K.A. Linde's billionaire romance Cruel Trilogy.</p> <p>Darkness swept in.</p> <p>Smothering everything in its inky black.</p> <p>In its wake, we became our own worst nightmares.</p> <p>How can we fight our way back?</p> <p>Do we even deserve to?</p>"; 
